NFPGenerator

Class MultiPolygon

  • java.lang.Object
    • NFPGenerator.MultiPolygon

  • public class MultiPolygon
extends java.lang.Object
    this class contains a polygon to be used to generate the no-fit polygon. The polygon exists of coordinates and can have holes in it.
    Author:
    Stiaan Uyttersprot
